Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:07.69,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Faint-hearted traveler, you should pull back now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.69,0:00:11.40,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Before you collapse
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:15.16,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}But you still say that you want to go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:21.91,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}To the other side of the distant sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:41.31,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Thousands of travelers have prayed to me before
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:48.86,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}After they collapsed at the other end of their journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:56.49,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}In a place that is not here, in a time that is not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.49,0:01:04.75,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}You're searching, saying that there's love there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:12.21,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Even though you could just patiently wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.21,0:01:17.47,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}For the destiny that I have given you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:22.35,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Do you know I'm a Venus?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.18,0:01:26.94,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Faint-hearted traveler, come closer to me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:30.82,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Come sit at my feet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:34.49,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I will embrace you and show you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:38.28,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}What is waiting beyond the distant sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:44.29,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}What you wanna go high? Make it heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:51.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:55.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On a spring night, Virgo is spread out widely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:02:01.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My favorite star, Spica, is this Alpha star.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you stretch this line from the Big\NDipper, there's the North Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:10.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And if you pull the handle of the ladle,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:14.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there's the star of the cow\Nherder, Arcturus, then Spica!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:20.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This line is called the Great Arc of Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:25.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}During the cherry blossom season,\Ntry looking for it in the southern sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:31.96,Fireworks,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord0.5\blur2\shad1.5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\pos(429,303)}What I Can Do For You Now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:39.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:42.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:46.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Shibata Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:49.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mother's currently hospitalized here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:50.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:56.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see... I collapsed, and then this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:59.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey... I overheard a little of what was going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:01.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a student of the Space School?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:03.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:07.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that you're from the newly\Nestablished Astronaut Training Course?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:09.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:11.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:14.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Asumi-chan's there too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:19.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see... she's having her\Nchildhood dreams come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:25.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're really Kamogawa-san's friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:28.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean... you didn't even know\Nwhich school she attended...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:31.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:32.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's strange, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:37.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi-chan was my friend from\Nwhen I was still living in Yuigahama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I ended up moving, and that\Nwas the end of it, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:43.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if she still remembers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:49.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, to me, she's a very dear\Nperson that I can't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:53.79,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\3c&H6A1C1B&\c&HC3EAE3&\bord0\fnPolo\frz16.88\blur0.9\pos(642,196)}Night on the Galactic Railroad\NMiyazawa Kenji
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:59.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though the distance\Nbetween us has widened,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:03.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,every time I see this leaf star,\NI've always remembered
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that Asumi-chan has always been with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:29.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? It ended...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The blood trails off here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:37.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If someone's here, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:38.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With this amount of blood,\Nif the person was hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:50.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:57.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to look for them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:59.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But where else am I supposed to look?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:11.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't even have a compass, so if I go around\Nsearching now, I might be the one that gets lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:14.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:16.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:19.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lion-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:26.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A leaf star?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:34.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There aren't any maple trees here,\Nso where did it come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:37.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Little one, you'll have to\Ndo all that you can do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:40.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like you've always done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That time, I really wanted to\Ndo more for Kasane-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:53.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but at the time, that was the best I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:56.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What I can do now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:58.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll go straight to the goal,\Nwithout taking any breaks to rest,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:01.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and then call for help there if it's needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:05.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If someone's here, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:09.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to hurry to the goal,\Nbut I'll come back as soon as I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:11.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So please wait until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:17.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's the possibility it really\Nisn't anything too serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:20.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In any case, I have to get to\Nthe goal as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:29.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:36.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she's such a dear friend to you, why didn't you\Ntry to stay in contact with her after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:39.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We didn't part under the best of circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:44.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see... because of the Lion\Naccident, my father died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:48.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I was also hospitalized for burns,\NI couldn't make any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:52.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi-chan was the only one\Nwho became friends with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:56.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I said a lot of horrible things...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:07:00.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi-chan didn't do anything wrong at all,\Nyet I said so many horrible things to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:05.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then before I had a chance to apologize,\Nwe suddenly decided to move,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:07.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and that was how it ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:11.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can you still say she's dear to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:18.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can you still say that\Nyou were always together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:21.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could just be that only\Nyou think of her that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:25.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She might still be angry\Nand might not forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:33.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah... that's true. It could\Njust be my own selfishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:36.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I don't know why... even\Nnow, I still believe in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:44.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, though I couldn't say it at the time, Asumi-chan\Nwas the one that gave me what I really wanted the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What you really wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:50.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:52.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A real friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:56.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A real friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:35.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Judging by how far I've gone,\NI should be close to the goal, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:50.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's only a little water left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:53.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll just have to endure without\Nit in case of an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can still endure a little further...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:20.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just a little bit more until the goal...\Njust a little bit more...
