Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:26.75,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(421.714,90.857)\bord0\fnHand of Diesel\c&H4A3B35&\blur1}Ukita Marika
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:26.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ukita-san, I see you've woken up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there any place that hurts?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:32.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:34.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll go call the doctor over then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:40.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'll take my leave here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:42.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:45.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't go yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:51.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I... I also have to apologize to Kamogawa-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:55.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I don't know if she'll forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:59.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I don't know what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:04.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She told me that I couldn't go to space alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:07.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She told me, "Let's go to space together," so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:09.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We promised it, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:10.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:11.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:15.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to apologize... I have to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:19.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it wouldn't be possible\Nfor us to become friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:24.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because... because no one needs me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was never wanted by anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:32.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I... I... I'm an unwanted child!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:38.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no one who's not needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:41.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:43.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did someone tell you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:46.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see... it must have been painful...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:50.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why am I crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:53.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's something I already know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:59.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you know, the words that come out of\Nsomeone's mouth aren't necessarily the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:03.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not everyone can express their\Nfeelings well in words.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:06.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's most important is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:17.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:21.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had someone who was my\Nsister as well as my mother
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:24.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who had the same name as me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:28.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never told this to anyone before
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because I was told not to,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:35.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but that person died, and I'm still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:39.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm actually here, but no one will look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:44.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you aren't needed where you\Nare right now, that's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:48.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It isn't anyone's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:53.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just that surely there is\Nsomeone that needs you somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:59.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the time comes, you just have to do the\Nbest you can to be of help to that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:00.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like Asumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:07.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've lived this entire time\Nthinking that, wanting to be like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:09.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The next time I get to meet Asumi-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:13.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to be someone who smiles,\Nwho can tell her that I'm doing my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:23.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when that happens, it doesn't matter\Nif Asumi-chan thinks I'm her friend or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:28.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I'll be happy if I see her,\Nbut it's all right if we can't meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:33.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She has always been inside\Nmy heart, looking after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:38.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're with Asumi-chan now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:42.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Treasure this time you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that be enough\Nfor you and Asumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:56.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ukita!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:12:58.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:00.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:02.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I see you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:11.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:25.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Judging from where I am right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:29.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,South is this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:33.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the goal is on that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:49.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm still all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:51.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's just a little further...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:08.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The goal area!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:11.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness! I made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:19.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:22.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi! Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:28.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:30.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:33.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:35.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuchuuya-kun and Suzuki-kun too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:36.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you're finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:39.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you guys just make it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.39,0:14:42.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, being\Nso easygoing about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:44.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All three of us made it here yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:48.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got worried because you were so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:49.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:51.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The others are on the other side of that flag
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:55.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with tents set up waiting\Nfor anyone who might be injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:15:01.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So then, everyone reached the goal.\NThank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:04.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even the person who got hurt got this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:11.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really... because of Kei's worrying, we had\Nto go back and forth from here to there seven times!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:12.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it was eight times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:15.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hearing that makes me more tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:19.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be quiet. You're the one\Nthat tagged along, Fucchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:22.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She got you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:24.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! Your glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:27.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't take so long to notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:29.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:29.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:31.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A compass...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong with this compass?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:37.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm? It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:38.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just a little surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:41.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surprised by what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it just missing in my capsule?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:50.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:52.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm tired as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:54.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's a good thing that it's been sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:16:00.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the weather had turned bad, it would have\Nbeen difficult in the forest without a compass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:02.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:06.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It couldn't be that the little seagull\Ncame all the way here without a compass...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:13.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will bring Ukita Marika back with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:14.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the current situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:27.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the students have arrived at location A.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:32.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right. Well then, start retrieving\Nthe capsules and the students now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:32.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:37.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Ukita Marika I met long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:40.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is the little one's friend, Ukita Marika.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:44.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the two are the same person,\NI can only think of one possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:49.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If she knows the secret of her birth...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:55.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ukita Marika, you are a very strong girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're with Asumi-chan now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:06.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Treasure this time you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that be enough\Nfor you and Asumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I dropped out from the training.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:18.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may be that I can't go\Nto space together with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:23.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:25.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm starving to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:26.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want some barbecue...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:29.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kalbi, salted tongue, liver slices...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:32.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't talk about food, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:37.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kei-chan, eat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:40.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why do you have so much, Asumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:42.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have quite a bit there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:44.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you feeling sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:48.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I had resolved to keep half\Nof it until I reached the goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:49.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:53.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:56.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm completely defeated by the little seagull.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:57.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you laughing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:18:00.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez! I don't get either of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:04.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you really don't mind if we eat this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:05.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:09.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi! I'll give you all my\NJapanese sweets from home for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:14.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kei-chan, was there anyone that was injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:17.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like someone who had a bloody wound...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:18.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:22.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one's eaten anything since\Nyesterday, so they're dead tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:25.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there wasn't anyone who was injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:27.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:32.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, on the way here, there\Nwas someone's capsule.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:34.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there were bloodstains there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:40.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's good that everyone\Nreached the goal safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:41.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:43.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's still one person who isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:44.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ukita-san still hasn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:48.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Marika-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:51.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't necessarily mean\Nthat was Marika...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:54.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't think of anything strange, Kamogawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:18:57.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:01.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no use going, little seagull.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She probably won't be there anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:04.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:08.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:10.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've noticed it too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:13.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a transmitter with personal data inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:18.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? S-so that's what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:22.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With these, all of the instructors\Nshould know where we are at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:24.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing I didn't lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:27.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd better get used to it soon,\Nthe way this school does things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:32.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So if Ukita-san had an immobilizing injury,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:35.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the rescue party would\Nhave already gotten to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:36.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:39.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, this is the last day\Nof the survival training.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:41.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you move away from the goal area now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:44.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you won't be able to return\Nhere by the end of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:48.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter what reason, it would\Nprobably be a great demerit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:50.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Demerit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:52.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as Shuu says, Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:53.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:59.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kamogawa, it could be that your dream\Nof going to space would be ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:01.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.17,0:20:02.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, we're going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:06.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm sure our ride back will come soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can finally go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:13.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I get back, it'll be barbecue for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:24.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What I can do now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:29.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:32.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Asumi, when we get back,\Non our next day off...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:34.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:35.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:39.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:40.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:44.09,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\fnSquare 721 Blk\c&H7F8B88&\bord1\3c&H262629&\}Tokyo National Space School
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:46.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei, there's something...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:47.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:49.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well... a student is moving away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:50.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:55.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is a student moving\Nfurther away from location A.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:57.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no sign of her stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:20:59.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is the name of the student?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:00.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's coming up right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:04.28,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\3c&H9E3843&\c&H9E3843&\frz11.68\4c&HD1E6E0&\shad1\move(399.11,13.78,408.89,42.22,26,1653)}Kamogawa Asumi
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.61,0:21:04.28,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur0.6\c&H5798C8&\frz11.68\4c&HD1E6E0&\move(399.11,13.78,408.89,42.22,26,1653)\shad1\4a&HFF&}Kamogawa Asumi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:04.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is Kamogawa Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:05.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:12.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is she trying to go,\Nafter having reached the goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hell if I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:15.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, bring her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:16.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:21.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Marika-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:28.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just how far did that dummy go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:32.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I forgot how fast she was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:33.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no hesitation in her run.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:40.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The little seagull clearly remembers\Nwhere she has gone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:44.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:50.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you guys all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:51.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:54.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it, what's that dummy thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.21,0:21:57.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About her friend, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:21:59.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:00.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, we're also the ones thinking about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.13,0:22:07.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:09.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really...
